
'''''Azali''''' ni film y'ikinamico yo muri [[Gana]]  yasohotse 2018 iyobowe na Kwabena Gyansah<ref>https://www.talkafricanmovies.com/azali/</ref> . Yatoranijwe muri [[Gana]] muri Filime Nziza Mpuzamahanga igaragara mu bihembo bya 92 Awards Academy, ariko ntabwo yatowe.  Bwari ubwambere [[Gana|Ghana]] itanga firime  nziza muri Oscar award<ref>https://afrocentriconline.ca/azali/</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Umukobwa ukiri muto, Amina, abana na nyina, nyirakuru na nyirarume mu mudugudu muto hanze ya Accra<ref>https://www.bellanaija.com/2020/01/kwabena-gyansah-azali/</ref>. Abaho ubuzima bwiza ariko burambiranye nyina yifuza kumubohora<ref>https://montrealblackfilm.com/en/movie/azali-fate-2/</ref>. Nyirakuru yifuriza Amina kurongora umusaza ukomoka mu mudugudu wabo<ref>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/2020-oscars-ghana-selects-azali-international-feature-film-category-1241298/</ref>. Nyina wa Amina arigaragambya kandi agurisha Amina ku muntu atazi atizeye ka  azabona ubuzima bwiza muri uyu mujyi<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film908257.html</ref>. Mu rugendo rwe Amina ahura numusore nawe wagurishijwe akiri umusore kandi muburyo bumwe, aba inshuti ye yonyine<ref>https://www.moviemeter.nl/film/1128543</ref>. Bombi bahunze hamwe nitsinda rito ry'abana nabo bagurishijwe. Mugihe bombi batangiye imirimo itandukanye binyuze muri Accra bagerageza kubona ibyo bakomeza<ref>https://culturecustodian.com/ghanas-oscar-2020-entry-azali-is-coming-to-netflix-next-week/</ref>.

